OL,3,CFerry worker endangered lives in fatal
OL,4,Cboat collision, jury finds
OL,6,FA Condor Ferry worker endangered lives
OL,7,Fafter the vessel collided with a
OL,8,Ffishing trawler - which resulted in
OL,9,Fthe deaths of three fishermen - a jury
OL,10,Fhas decided.
OL,12,FLewis Peter Carr, from Sunderland, was
OL,13,Funanimously found guilty of
OL,14,Fendangering ships, structures, or
OL,15,Findividuals, contrary to Jersey's
OL,16,FShipping Law - the offence carries a
OL,17,Fmaximum sentence of two years.
