OL,3,CFerry worker endangered lives in fatal
OL,4,Cboat collision, jury finds
OL,6,FHe was the Second Officer and in
OL,7,Fcharge at the time of the collision
OL,8,Fbetween the Commodore Goodwill Condor
OL,9,FFerry and L'Ecume II fishing trawler
OL,10,Fin December 2022.
OL,12,FCarr was assigned to the bridge
OL,13,Falongside Artur Sevash-Zade, a
OL,14,FUkrainian national.
OL,16,FThey were each accused of three counts
OL,17,Fof manslaughter and the fourth lesser
OL,18,Fcount of endangerment - the pair
OL,19,Fdenied all the charges.
