OL,3,CFerry worker endangered lives in fatal
OL,4,Cboat collision, jury finds
OL,6,FCarr was discharged of the
OL,7,Fmanslaughter charges after the jury
OL,8,Ffailed to reach a verdict.
OL,10,FMr Sevash-Zade was found not guilty of
OL,11,Fthe manslaughter charges and formally
OL,12,Fdischarged of the fourth, lesser
OL,13,Fcharge as the jury could not reach a
OL,14,Fverdict.
OL,16,FJersey's Royal Court has heard
OL,17,Fevidence over the past three weeks
OL,18,Fabout the incident between Condor's
OL,19,FCommodore Goodwill and the L'Ecume II
OL,20,Fin the early hours of 9 December 2022.
