OL,3,CFerry worker endangered lives in fatal
OL,4,Cboat collision, jury finds
OL,6,FThe crew of the L'Ecume II - Skipper
OL,7,FMichael Michieli, and crew members
OL,8,FJervis Baligat, and Larry Simyunn -
OL,9,Fwere on board the vessel when it sank.
OL,11,FAll died following the collision.
OL,13,FCommissioner Sir John Saunders - the
OL,14,Fpresiding judge - said that this had
OL,15,Fbeen "an extraordinarily difficult
OL,16,Fcase".
OL,18,FHe added: "It was, I'm afraid, always
OL,19,Fgoing to be difficult. I have been
OL,20,Fvery grateful for the efforts (the
OL,21,Fjury) made in this case.
