OL,6,F"Thank you very much for your
OL,7,Fattendance and the hard work you've
OL,8,Fput into this."
OL,10,FAndy Shearwood, the Senior
OL,11,FInvestigating Officer for the incident
OL,12,F- titled Operation Nectar - described
OL,13,Fit as "one of the most complex
OL,14,Finvestigations that the States of
OL,15,FJersey Police has ever had to deal
OL,16,Fwith".
OL,18,FHe continued: "One of the most
OL,19,Fchallenging aspects of this
OL,20,Finvestigation was the crime scene.
