OL,6,F"L'Ecume sank immediately - it was
OL,7,Freally, really difficult to access the
OL,8,Fboat itself, but we were really
OL,9,Fconscious of some of the valuable
OL,10,Fevidence it could have provided."
OL,12,FThroughout the trial, the court heard
OL,13,Fabout Mr Michieli's habits regarding
OL,14,Fthe display of his fishing lights.
OL,16,FIf they were on - which witnesses said
OL,17,Fthey always were - that meant Michael
OL,18,Fhad right of way. But if they were
OL,19,Fnot, it was his vessel that needed to
OL,20,Fmove.
