OL,3,CFerry worker endangered lives in fatal
OL,4,Cboat collision, jury finds
OL,6,FCarr said he believed the collision
OL,7,Fhappened because L'Ecume II did not
OL,8,Fdisplay its fishing lights, there was
OL,9,Fno effective lookout on the trawler,
OL,10,Fand because the fishing vessel altered
OL,11,Fcourse in a port direction in the
OL,12,Ffinal minutes before the collision.
OL,14,FThis, Carr said, was not compliant
OL,15,Fwith the International Regulations for
OL,16,FPreventing Collisions at Sea.
