OL,3,CFerry worker endangered lives in fatal
OL,4,Cboat collision, jury finds
OL,6,FThe defendant also told the court that
OL,7,Fhe believed the collision was
OL,8,Favoidable - but he felt he was
OL,9,Fcomplying with regulations in his
OL,10,Factions.
OL,12,FRobin Smith, States of Jersey Police
OL,13,FChief Officer, stated that his
OL,14,Fthoughts were with "the bereaved
OL,15,Ffamilies and friends who have
OL,16,Fexhibited remarkable dignity despite
OL,17,Ftheir loss".
OL,19,FHe also called Operation Nectar the
OL,20,Fforce's "largest and most complex
OL,21,Finvestigation in its history".
