OL,4,Cboat collision, jury finds
OL,6,FHe added: "I am very proud of the
OL,7,Fofficers and staff who have worked so
OL,8,Fhard on this major incident. From a
OL,9,Fstanding start, they have immersed
OL,10,Fthemselves in complex maritime law,
OL,11,Ftechnology, policy and procedures.
OL,13,F"They have worked tirelessly, taking
OL,14,Fhundreds of statements, interviewing
OL,15,Fover 150 witnesses, examining around
OL,16,F800 documents, and seizing over 1000
OL,17,Fexhibits.
