OL,3,CFerry worker endangered lives in fatal
OL,4,Cboat collision, jury finds
OL,6,F"The dedication of our team of Family
OL,7,FLiaison Officers over the last few
OL,8,Fyears often goes unnoticed, but their
OL,9,Fcontribution deserves recognition.
OL,11,F"Recent history shows that when faced
OL,12,Fwith tragedy, islanders, agencies and
OL,13,Forganisations come together. Very
OL,14,Fcomplex cases like this cannot be
OL,15,Fdelivered without an island-wide
OL,16,Feffort."
OL,18,FJersey's fishing and wider community
OL,19,Fis still coming to terms with the
OL,20,Fdeath of Mr Michieli and his two crew
OL,21,Fmembers, Mr Simyunn and Mr Baligat.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G12/14
