OL,3,CFerry worker endangered lives in fatal
OL,4,Cboat collision, jury finds
OL,6,FMr Shearwood explained: "It was really
OL,7,Femotional on the day Michael was
OL,8,Frecovered. We were several days into
OL,9,Fthe recovery operation. Even then, the
OL,10,Fweather window was starting to close,
OL,11,Fand we didn't know if we would ever
OL,12,Frecover him."
OL,14,FChristopher Le Masurier, Managing
OL,15,FDirector of the Jersey Oyster Company,
OL,16,Fdescribed Mr Michieli as a "prominent"
OL,17,Ffigure in the fishing industry.
OL,19,FHe added: "It's still a shock for him
OL,20,Fnot to be there, and his boat was
OL,21,Falways a pleasure to see.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G13/14
