OL,6,F"We'd be at sea, we'd arrange to meet
OL,7,Fup with our French colleagues, and
OL,8,Fthat's just a tribute to the big heart
OL,9,Fthat Michael had, and the respect that
OL,10,Fpeople had for him."
OL,12,FLewis Peter Carr will be sentenced on
OL,13,FThursday 4 December.
